{"tid":2197037,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"耿爽狠嗆美國：公然站在世界各國的對立面的「恥辱」","createTime":"2020-09-10T10:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T11:46:07.000Z","uid":337052,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9b6ec8ad64f7dd74ad29a7cc6dec404f3f745384","tid":2197037,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:20:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">視訊交鋒！美方批中國該對疫情蔓延負責 耿爽當場跳腳回嗆</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/09/10/php0tY7Of.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F09%2F10%2Fphp0tY7Of.jpg&h=50f82e12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聯合國安理會於當地時間9日舉辦視訊會議，美國代表在會中指責中國「抗疫不透明」，批中國對疫情蔓延負有責任，此言讓耿爽（見圖）跳腳駁斥，稱美國傳播政治病毒，發言充滿政治惡意，中方表示堅決反對。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n2020/09/10 17:28<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕聯合國安理會於當地時間9日針對武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫情應對舉辦視訊會議，美國代表在會中指責中國「抗疫不透明」，批中國對疫情蔓延負有責任，此言讓中國常駐聯合國副代表耿爽跳腳駁斥，稱美國傳播政治病毒，發言充滿政治惡意，中方表示堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，聯合國安理會針對武漢肺炎疫情應對，展開視訊會議，沒想到美中兩方代表在會議上展開交鋒，美方代表先發言指責，中方抗疫不透明、處置不當，批中國對疫情蔓延負有責任。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽隨即跳腳駁斥，強調中方短時間就控制疫情，也第一時間就向世界衛生組織及包含美國在內的多國通報疫情，並公佈新冠病毒基因序列，為全球抗疫鬥爭做出重大貢獻；他自豪說道，中國努力、貢獻得到聯合國、世界衛生組織以及國際社會的普遍認可。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">耿爽反嗆美國確診最多，醫療條件最先進卻不集中精神抗疫，試圖轉移焦點嫁禍他人，直批這是「恥辱」</span>；他更用一連串詞語連珠炮轟炸<span class=\"red\">「將疫情政治化、污名化、標籤化，自私自利、混淆是非、轉嫁責任、諉過於人，挽救不了生命，更不能控制疫情，最終只會搬起石頭砸自己的腳」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">耿爽認為美國除了嫁禍中國，還無故指責世界衛生組織，「公然站在世界各國的對立面」；耿爽直批，美國濫用安理會平台，濫用安理會會議來傳播「政治病毒」，是為了服務美國國內的政治，發言充滿政治惡意，中方表示堅決反對，也完全拒絕。</span><br />\n<br />\n完整聯合國會議影片，耿爽回應約49分11秒處<br />\n<a href=\"http://webtv.un.org/watch/player/6189257830001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwebtv.un.org%2Fwatch%2Fplayer%2F6189257830001&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FM70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=294ffd61\" target=\"_blank\">http://webtv.un.org/watch/player/6189257830001</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3287834\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3287834&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FM70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=8dbcfa16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3287834&h=f57a3ce5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3287834</a>"},{"pid":"f4b675dec28ff31ea6e6fa2fbe67ba3738946fe8","tid":2197037,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgur.dcard.tw/wBwLpnOh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.dcard.tw%2FwBwLpnOh.jpg&h=a44dcc62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d6b447960f101595d9608f88476ca97454f64f0","tid":2197037,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:23:15.000Z","msg":"樓主法輪功打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc576228e88f003eeca915a93b3fcabe349f570","tid":2197037,"uid":82912,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:23:41.000Z","msg":"條友唔係去左美國咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73de44f850017418eec74fc38559b5ab8fb9923e","tid":2197037,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:25:04.000Z","msg":"阿爽翻來囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698cb9c9e62c1d2f19e39dea238b68c3d8ee4832","tid":2197037,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:25:37.000Z","msg":"朝鮮又名各國， 肯雅又名世界"},{"pid":"1ad936b7e87ef8ebfa1bfd1ba6eac579ac36c29f","tid":2197037,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:25:42.000Z","msg":"有番阿爽 加速既感覺又番返黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63639f614879856c97e1858b812459c868b194f4","tid":2197037,"uid":275370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:27:01.000Z","msg":"恥夾：汪汪汪汪汪"},{"pid":"b9369d58021d9a960bdb0793e35ee8e631cb3cbb","tid":2197037,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:27:28.000Z","msg":"安理會中美交鋒! 美控中國要對全球疫情負責 耿爽 : 你才傳播政治病毒<br />\n新頭殼newtalk | 李志良 綜合報導<br />\n發布 2020.09.10 | 11:23<br />\n     <br />\n<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/464/5f599b57ed328.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F464%2F5f599b57ed328.png&h=87368213&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國常駐聯合國副代表耿爽。   圖 : 翻攝自CCTV<br />\n<br />\n聯合國安理會美國代表於當地時間9月9日在公開視訊會議上指責中國應對全球武漢肺炎疫情負責，中國常駐聯合國副代表耿爽則立即反駁，稱美國才在散播政治病毒，企圖轉嫁責任，諉過於人。<br />\n<br />\n安理會9日舉行視頻公開會，討論安理會涉新冠疫情第2532號決議落實情況。美國代表在發言中指責中方抗疫不透明、處置不當，對疫情在全球蔓延負有責任。 耿爽當場要求再次發言對美方予以駁斥。<br />\n<br />\n「美國政府應該把時間和精力放在保障美國人民身體健康和生命安全上，而不是轉嫁責任，諉過於人。」耿爽說。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n耿爽稱，美國代表剛才的發言完全是在濫用安理會平臺，濫用安理會會議，是在傳播政治病毒，服務其國內政治。 耿爽批評，美國代表的發言充滿政治惡意和肆意攻擊，企圖政治化、汙名化，中方對此表示堅決反對和完全拒絕，相信多數安理會成員對此也不認同。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽表示，新冠肺炎疫情發生後，中方本著公開、透明、負責任態度，及時有效採取全面措施，在短時間內控制住疫情。中方第一時間向世界衛生組織和包括美國在內的很多國家通報分享疫情資訊，並公佈新冠病毒基因序列，為全球抗疫鬥爭做出重大貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽反擊，反觀美國，作為世界上醫療條件最發達最先進的國家，現在卻是全球疫情確診人數最多的國家。這個國家的政府不集中精力抗疫，卻一直試圖轉移視線，嫁禍於人。這簡直是個恥辱。將疫情政治化、汙名化、標籤化，自私自利、混淆是非、轉嫁責任、諉過於人，挽救不了生命，更不能控制疫情，最終只會搬起石頭砸自己的腳。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽說，中方敦促美國政府切實負起責任，把時間和精力放在保障美國人民的身體健康和生命安全上。中方對美國民眾遭受的苦難深表同情，他們是美國政府政治操弄的最大受害者。中國祝福美國人民早日戰勝疫情，恢復正常生活。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">耿爽強調，美國不僅嫁禍中國，還無端指責世界衛生組織，公然站在世界各國的對立面。在這個問題上，美國完全是冒天下之大不韙，成了孤家寡人。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-09-10/463307\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-09-10%2F463307&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FM70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=5e62733c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-09-10/463307</a>"},{"pid":"c93173417abf0c58e8d84d589e27f5097526e439","tid":2197037,"uid":227271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:28:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UgKCgqO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUgKCgqO.jpg&h=af93b9e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4491aa227d0e970dc4f20a14b7e6becd2b3f1335","tid":2197037,"uid":58911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:31:07.000Z","msg":"小粉紅：666 爽哥懟得好<br />\n<br />\n被代表的各國：？？？"},{"pid":"03c56e545fda0cdc8aacb2609aee9f0efe4d0197","tid":2197037,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:31:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">美代表指責中國對疫情蔓延負有責任！ 耿爽「很不爽」當場怒斥</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5130/5130393.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5130%2F5130393.jpg&h=0bd9b7f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3304eb8e4cc5c40739bd9c110c4b0c2ad8817650","tid":2197037,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03c56e545fda0cdc8aacb2609aee9f0efe4d0197","tid":2197037,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:31:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">美代表指責中國對疫情蔓延負有責任！ 耿爽「很不爽」當場怒斥</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5130/5130393.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5130%2F5130393.jpg&h=0bd9b7f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:33:19.000Z","msg":"原來派佢去UN就真係為左face2face口交 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3688fb5a7b846aad574d1eb0ae187a407755f398","tid":2197037,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:34:47.000Z","msg":"中國 = 世界 <im